{"tid":2299104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯疫苗保護率逾九成 售價低於10美元","createTime":"2020-11-24T13:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T21:40:19.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dfdecdbe6e6ebef582368b4c393d05c97d6604b8","tid":2299104,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯新冠疫苗保護率逾九成 售價低於10美元<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯新型冠狀病毒疫苗「衛星V」官方Twitter表示， 第二次臨床測試中期分析結果顯示，在注射首劑「衛星V」疫苗後第28天，疫苗有效性為91.4％，注射首劑42天後有效性超過95％。研究有逾1.8萬志願者參與，測試期間未有出現預期以外的不良反應現象。疫苗生產商又表示，一劑疫苗在國際市場售價將低於10美元，將繼續擴大與國際其他生產伙伴的合作協議，預料明年可為全球超過5億人提供疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯公民將可免費接種「衛星V」疫苗。副總理戈利科娃表示，當局計劃明年開始為國民大規模接種，但強調接種屬自願性質。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367731&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKPsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=bc18d436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367731</a>"},{"pid":"6c66f87cce87b55ac0373bc6a85a209c6a130c4d","tid":2299104,"uid":277702,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"但死亡率可能高過中武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb06af541de410033ee98d2f673f4b8b89ce465f","tid":2299104,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"俄佬 D 軍事科技好似唔錯<br />\n生物科技就唔清楚"},{"pid":"2565ad01186c8423aa7d23697d1cbe1654768d80","tid":2299104,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"有效率九成<br />\n（只限戰鬥民族）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd29e64c4703f1728fbfe985b0329d92e8cd5bb","tid":2299104,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{